{"tid":1390658,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"八成南韓人表示：不再支持C.朗拿度","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T12:13:48.000Z","uid":82938,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6b529f86f97c658d0768f5e55d0636ba6b51ce80","tid":1390658,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"八成南韓人表示：不再支持C.朗拿度<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n2019 07月31日14:48<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\nC.朗拿度事件<br />\n<br />\n　　直播吧7月31日訊 據韓媒MBC Sports調查，八成南韓人表示，不會再支持C.朗拿度。<br />\n　　C.朗拿度在訪韓友誼賽中未登場，引起南韓國民不滿。7月30日，南韓19歲以上的501名民眾接受了調查，79.4%的人選擇了「以後不再為C.朗拿度加油」，「今後還會繼續為C.朗拿度助威」的僅佔9.3%。<br />\n　　參加調查的球迷中45.9%（約230人）曾是C.朗拿度的球迷，其中85.6%表示不再支持C.朗拿度。<br />\n　　針對該事件責任方在誰，25.3%球迷選擇了南韓職業足球聯盟，22.7%球迷選C.朗拿度，18.3%球迷選祖記，17.3%球迷選主辦方。<br />\n　　（直播吧）"},{"pid":"091d69a8b7f607442b2aa4b0ede35f49edd94dff","tid":1390658,"uid":53828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:39:10.000Z","msg":"小器"},{"pid":"b36d61374c3ceff2d68c39bb873ac09c9d0af1f2","tid":1390658,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"091d69a8b7f607442b2aa4b0ede35f49edd94dff","tid":1390658,"uid":53828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:39:10.000Z","msg":"小器"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"違約<br />\n無品"},{"pid":"5511b8522e04c73aa1cc430224a60e533f02400e","tid":1390658,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:58:06.000Z","msg":"find Son la diu"},{"pid":"6a3b11cc41854e140204059e87cc57526d45d51b","tid":1390658,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9400f97811ac38ff952cc702f472c728a90890bf","tid":1390658,"uid":56459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"Who cares"},{"pid":"a063a51d0e6c8639caa241759115eb743444f03b","tid":1390658,"uid":1259